item.title: CVE-2020-14560|2024-09-27T18:40:31.056Z -- oracle%20corporation -- hyperion%20bi%2B
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle Hyperion BI+ product of Oracle Hyperion (component: UI and Visualization). The supported version that is affected is 11.1.2.4. Difficult to exploit vulnerability allows high privileged attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle Hyperion BI+. Successful attacks require human interaction from a person other than the attacker. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized access to critical data or complete access to all Oracle Hyperion BI+ accessible data. CVSS 3.1 Base Score 4.2 (Confidentiality impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:H/PR:H/UI:R/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N).
